{
  "stem": "12051.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I started to support his elbow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw he is fainting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because everything was so raw yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just couldn't cope with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After what you have gone through, the fear of all those years-- you know, so many times you think to yourself, is it humanly possible that you can go through such hell and remain sane, and sing, and want to accomplish, and want to achieve?",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you want to have a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everything becomes important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It doesn't make sense to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I sometimes wonder, how come you get attached again to things that are very unimportant in life?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It proved to me that those things are not important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Important was my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If I would have had my brother, my whole life would have meant something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Picture it, that finally we decided to have children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I was-- at that time, I was very rebellious, and so was David.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were-- and the need to call God to [NON-ENGLISH], that he owes us something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- he has to answer why he did-- why he killed the nicest people and he left me alive?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't deserve that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But God didn't answer me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I didn't want to be religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I-- I wanted to be rebellious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But when I became pregnant, we sat down one day and said, what now?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "How do we raise our children?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In which direction are we going?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we decided that being that my father died, and my brother died, and my whole family died for the reason that they were Jews-- for no other reason and never committed a crime.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were only born in the wrong place.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
